titleStmt.title: The arraignment and acquittal of Sr. Edward Mosely Baronet, indited at the Kings bench bar for a rape, upon the body of Mistris Anne Swinnerton. Ianuary 28, 1647. / Taken by a reporter there present, who heard all the circumstances thereof, whereof this is a true copy.

notesStmt.note: Reproduction of the original in the British Library.
